data.description: Welcome to this charming home, this beautiful residence boasts 2 bedrooms, 2 baths with upgrades for modern comfort that seamlessly blend with classic charm. The main floor invites you in as the spaciousness allows you to greet your guests in style. The main floor is designed for both entertaining and relaxation. This floor features a expansive living room with ample windows letting the sun stream in, creating a bright airy space. The dining room is a hosting space for large and small gatherings and it serves as an ideal setting for making cherished memories. The kitchen is inviting with tons of storage and ample counter tops for cooking. The kitchen leads out to the back of the home overlooking a beautiful fenced backyard where you can relax and enjoy serenity on the patio. Upstairs you will find two massive bedrooms and a full bath with preserved classic tiles. The primary bedroom is expansive with a separate space for reading and huge closets. When you head downstairs you will find a large family room,  finished off with recessed lighting and multiple bonus areas with tons of storage.  The lower bathroom is also modernized and beautiful.  The utilities are newer and well maintained through diligent maintenance schedules. The owner did multiple upgrades of lighting, updating bathrooms, and modernizing the basement, come see it while it lasts, you're ideal home waits for you on this wonderful block.
